Soy sauce is ubiquitous throughout Japan and the world. 

But few know about the ancient origins of the holy grail of Japanese cuisine.

Carefully climbing the steep stairs,I followed Tsunenori Kano into the loft of the fermentation room of his family's 180-year-old soy sauce brewery, Kadocho. 
1.看逗號 劃動詞 介系詞 切短句
Carefully climbing the steep stairs =>小心地爬上很陡的樓梯，
          ^^^^^^^^
2.I followed Tsunenori Kano into the loft of the fermentation room 
    ^^^^^^^^                ^^^^              
我跟隨Tsunenori Kano進入發酵室的閣樓

3.of his family's 180-year-old soy sauce brewery, Kadocho. 
他家180年歷史的醬油釀造廠"Kadocho"
		  
4.整句=>小心地爬上很陡的樓梯，我跟隨Tsunenori Kano進入他家擁有180年歷史的醬油釀造廠"Kadocho"
的發酵室閣樓.

The dark space was eerily silent except for the creaking of my steps on the old wooden boards laid between the vats of soy sauce. 
               ^^^               ^^^^^^^^^^                          ^^                            ^^^^^^^     
1.看逗號 劃動詞 介系詞 切短句
The dark space was eerily silent =>黑暗的空間裡出奇地寂靜

2.except for the creaking of my steps=>除了我的腳步聲         

3.on the old wooden boards laid between the vats of soy sauce. 
  ^^                            ^^^^^^^
踩在大醬油桶間的舊木板上

4.整句=>黑暗的空間裡出奇地寂靜,除了我踩在大醬油桶間的舊木板上的腳步聲.

The soy sauce was now dormant, it being late winter, but it still filled the air with a savoury aroma. 
              ^^^                 ^^^^^                           ^^^^^^         ^^^^                    
1.看逗號 劃動詞 介系詞 切短句
The soy sauce was now dormant,=>醬油已經存封了.
              ^^^  
2.it being late winter=>已經是隆冬的季節
     ^^^^^
3.but it still filled the air with a savoury aroma. =>但空氣中依舊漫著濃郁的香氣。
               ^^^^^^         ^^^^  
4.整句=>已經是隆冬的季節,醬油已經存封了,但空氣中依舊漫著濃郁的香氣。

Around me, a thick, fungus-laden crust covered the ceiling, hung from the beams and grew up the walls.
                                       ^^^^^^^
1.看逗號 劃動詞 介系詞 切短句;a thick是補充的形容詞,說明fungus-laden
									   
Around me, a thick, fungus-laden crust covered the ceiling,
                   (主              詞)^^^^^^^
=>在我周圍,天花板上蓋上一層厚厚的充滿真菌的外殼

2.hung from the beams and grew up the walls.
掛在橫樑上，並在牆壁上長大。

3.整句=>在我周圍,天花板上蓋上一層厚厚的充滿真菌的外殼,掛在橫樑上，並在牆壁上長大。